title: Meta Trader 4 Trading Systems
description:
Collection of over 300 trading systems.

Instruction.

1. Download Meta Trader 4 from the following website. http://www.metatrader4.com/

2. Open a demo account.

3. Install your chosen system by following the instruction. In the file there will be indicators and possibly a template file.

4. In Meta Trader go to file then Data File, and install your indicators. Your indicators generally go to Expert Advisors - Indicators. Templates go to the template folder.

5. Once your strategy is successful, open a real account and Good luck!!

PS Its possible to automate your strategy by writing an Expert advisor. Another method is using the following panel from the following website: 
https://www.mql5.com/en/market/product/9602
